39:09.667 --> 39:10.542
IT WASN'T ME THAT WAS
HOLDING YOU BACK FROM IT.

39:10.542 --> 39:13.500
PACEY, YOU'VE
NEVER HELD ME BACK.

39:13.500 --> 39:15.500
YOU HAVE TO STOP
THINKING LIKE THAT.

39:15.500 --> 39:17.500
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I COULD STOP THINKING LIKE THAT

39:17.500 --> 39:19.583
IF YOU'D JUST
PROMISE ME ONE THING,

39:19.583 --> 39:21.834
THAT IF THE DAY EVER COMES,

39:21.834 --> 39:24.667
AND IT MAY COME MUCH SOONER
THAN EITHER ONE OF US THINKS,

39:24.667 --> 39:30.458
BUT IF THAT DAY EVER COMES
WHERE YOU DID FEEL LIKE
I WAS HOLDING YOU BACK...

39:30.458 --> 39:32.750
PROMISE ME THAT YOU'D
CUT ME LOOSE, YEAH?

39:32.750 --> 39:34.041
PACEY.

39:34.041 --> 39:35.291
PROMISE ME THAT.

39:35.291 --> 39:36.959
I WON'T
PROMISE YOU THAT.

39:36.959 --> 39:39.625
YOU'RE ASKING ME
TO PROMISE
TO LET YOU GO.

39:43.500 --> 39:45.792
I CAN'T DO THAT.

39:53.875 --> 39:55.708
EXACTLY WHAT IS IT
WE'RE DOING, AGAIN?

39:55.708 --> 39:57.333
I TOLD YOU.
A MEMORY EXERCISE.

39:57.333 --> 39:59.375
AND WHY ARE
WE DOING THIS?

39:59.375 --> 40:01.875
MY SHRINK
RECOMMENDED IT.

40:02.708 --> 40:04.458
IT'S KIND OF LIKE
SELF-HYPNOSIS.

40:04.458 --> 40:07.333
SUPPOSEDLY, IF YOU
STARE AT THE FISH

40:07.333 --> 40:10.083
FOR A HALF-HOUR OR SO,
IT WILL HELP YOU
REMEMBER THINGS.

40:10.083 --> 40:12.375
IT'S MY HOPE
THAT BY STARING AT THIS FISH,

40:12.375 --> 40:15.000
IT'LL HELP ME RECALL
WHY I'M SO ANGRY AT MY FATHER,

40:15.000 --> 40:17.792
THUS ALLOWING ME
TO FORGIVE BOTH HE AND MYSELF

40:17.792 --> 40:20.417
AND ENABLING US TO GO
TO SCHOOL IN NEW YORK CITY

40:20.417 --> 40:22.291
IF IN FACT THAT'S
WHERE WE DESIRE TO ATTEND.

40:22.291 --> 40:23.834
I SEE.

40:25.083 --> 40:27.750
NOT FOR NOTHING,
JEN, BUT, UM...

40:27.750 --> 40:29.583
IT'S ONLY SINCE
YOU STARTED SEEING
THIS PSYCHOLOGIST

40:29.583 --> 40:30.834
THAT I'M
STARTING TO THINK

40:30.834 --> 40:33.917
THAT YOU MAY
IN FACT BE CRAZY.

40:33.917 --> 40:36.792
JACK, DO YOU WANT
TO GO TO SCHOOL
IN NEW YORK?

40:36.792 --> 40:37.959
YEAH.

40:37.959 --> 40:40.000
SHUT UP.
WATCH THE FISH.

40:52.166 --> 40:53.625
DAWSON?

40:57.083 --> 40:58.375
HEY.

40:58.375 --> 40:59.792
HEY.

40:59.792 --> 41:01.333
BESSIE TOLD ME
I COULD WAIT
OUT HERE.

41:01.333 --> 41:02.542
I HOPE IT'S OK.

41:02.542 --> 41:05.875
YEAH, I'M JUST
A LITTLE SURPRISED,
CONSIDERING...

41:05.875 --> 41:08.291
I THINK YOU
UNDERESTIMATE ME.

41:09.667 --> 41:11.792
I THINK
WE UNDERESTIMATE
EACH OTHER.

41:13.959 --> 41:16.750
WHAT I'M TRYING
TO SAY, JOEY,
IS THAT...

41:19.959 --> 41:21.125
WHAT YOU FELT
THE OTHER NIGHT AT
THE MOVIE THEATER,

41:21.125 --> 41:24.417
THAT SOMETHING WAS
FINALLY RIGHT
BETWEEN US...

41:26.166 --> 41:27.917
I FELT THAT, TOO.

41:29.708 --> 41:31.667
AND NOTHING WILL
EVER CHANGE THAT--

41:31.667 --> 41:33.542
NOT GOING TO SCHOOL
ON DIFFERENT COASTS.

41:33.542 --> 41:35.166
NOT MEETING PEOPLE
WHO WE'RE MEANT
TO LOVE FOREVER--

41:35.166 --> 41:37.792
NOTHING.

41:37.792 --> 41:40.083
AND I WANT YOU
TO HAVE THIS.

41:42.083 --> 41:43.667
BUT, DAWSON--

41:43.667 --> 41:45.000
I DON'T KNOW
HOW I FEEL

41:45.000 --> 41:46.667
ABOUT YOU SLEEPING
WITH PACEY.

41:46.667 --> 41:48.792
I DON'T KNOW HOW
I'LL FEEL TOMORROW

41:48.792 --> 41:50.625
OR NEXT WEEK
OR NEXT YEAR
FOR THAT MATTER,

41:50.625 --> 41:53.792
BUT I'M
ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN

41:53.792 --> 41:56.792
THAT GIVING YOU THIS
IS THE RIGHT THING
TO DO.

41:58.875 --> 42:00.583
BECAUSE I'M
CERTAIN ABOUT US...

42:00.583 --> 42:03.417
AND WHAT WE MEAN
TO EACH OTHER.

42:06.834 --> 42:08.792
AND I THINK
YOU ARE, TOO.

42:18.000 --> 42:20.458
THANK YOU.

42:29.708 --> 42:32.500
YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE SOME OF
THE BEST YEARS

42:32.500 --> 42:33.667
OF YOUR LIFE
AT WORTHINGTON.

42:37.417 --> 42:38.417
AND I WANT TO HEAR
ALL ABOUT 'EM.
